Sentencas: A non-sealed solid oxide fuel cell stack with cells embedded in plane configuration was fabricated and operated successfully in a box-like stainless-steel chamber.
Titulo: Evaluation of a Non-sealed Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack with Cells Embedded in Plane Configuration

Sentencas: For a two-cell stack, it demonstrated an open circuit voltage (OCV) of 2.13?V and a maximum power output of 569?mW at the flow rate of 67?sccm CH4 and 33?sccm O2.
Titulo: Evaluation of a Non-sealed Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack with Cells Embedded in Plane Configuration

Sentencas: A fuel utilization of 4.16% was obtained.
Titulo: Evaluation of a Non-sealed Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack with Cells Embedded in Plane Configuration

Sentencas: The cell performance was dominated by two different mechanisms, the polarization of the cathode at low current and the concentration polarization of the anode at high current.
Titulo: Evaluation of a Non-sealed Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack with Cells Embedded in Plane Configuration

Sentencas: Finally, a scaled-up stack with six cells in series generated an OCV of 6.4?V and a maximum power output of 8.18?W.
Titulo: Evaluation of a Non-sealed Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack with Cells Embedded in Plane Configuration
